---
ksa_id: xr_production_workflow_asset_optimization
label: XR Production Workflow & Asset Optimization
category: Technical
sector: Immersive_Media_ARVR
horizon: core_2025
cluster_tags: ["XR Production","Pipeline","Asset Optimization"]
description: Managing end‑to‑end extended‑reality (XR) content pipelines—3D asset creation, optimization, versioning—to deliver high‑performance experiences across mobile, standalone, and tethered devices.
source_frameworks: ["OpenXR Specification","Unity XR Production Guidelines","Epic Games Unreal Engine VR Optimization Guide"]
proficiency_levels:
  - level: Awareness
    indicator: Imports models into game engines; recognises polygon‑count versus performance trade‑offs; understands basic baking.
  - level: Basic
    indicator: Applies Level‑of‑Detail (LOD) systems; compresses textures; tests build size against target hardware.
  - level: Intermediate
    indicator: Sets up automated asset‑pipeline scripts; profiles CPU/GPU performance; optimizes lighting via baked Global Illumination (GI).
  - level: Advanced
    indicator: Manages version control (Git/LFS) for large assets; implements asset‑bundling and streaming; establishes continuous‑integration build farm.
  - level: Expert
    indicator: Leads multi‑studio XR productions; standardises cross‑platform asset guidelines; publishes optimization benchmarks.
---